<H3> <TI>     Differences in CIS Countries' Currency Management Discussed </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Differences in CIS Countries' Currency Management Discussed </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944E0641A Moscow KOMMERSANT-DAILY in Russian 19 Mar 94 p 5 </F>
<F P=103> 944E0641A </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow KOMMERSANT-DAILY </F>
