<H5>  The Consumer Market </H5>
  Prices for consumer goods continued to rise in 
January in all Commonwealth states. The greatest rises in the 
level of prices in organized trade as compared with December 
1993 were registered in Azerbaijan, Armenia, Belarus, 
Kazakhstan, and Moldova. Changes in retail prices in the 
Commonwealth countries in January are characterized by the 
following data: 


------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|                         |January 1994 in relation to                        | 
