<H3> <TI>   NKR Official Denies Azeri Prisoner Mistreatment Allegations </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    NKR Official Denies Azeri Prisoner Mistreatment Allegations </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944K0988A Yerevan RESPUBLIKA ARMENIYA in Russian 29 Mar 94 p 
1 </F>

