<H3> <TI>   Supreme Soviet Session Reviews Political, Economic Issues </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Supreme Soviet Session Reviews Political, Economic Issues </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944K0988B Yerevan RESPUBLIKA ARMENIYA in Russian 29 Mar 94 p 
1 </F>

