<H3> <TI>   Ambassador to Moscow on Relations with Russia </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Ambassador to Moscow on Relations with Russia </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944K0941A Tbilisi SAKARTVELOS RESPUBLIKA in Georgian 9 Feb 
