<H3> <TI>   Finnish Daily on Russian Minority's Views, Goals </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Finnish Daily on Russian Minority's Views, Goals </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944K0897A Helsinki HUFVUDSTADSBLADET in Swedish 9 Mar 94 pp 
1, 3 </F>

<F P=103> 944K0897A </F>
<F P=104>  Helsinki HUFVUDSTADSBLADET </F>
