<H3> <TI>     Amount of Ukraine's Debts to CIS Countries Detailed </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Amount of Ukraine's Debts to CIS Countries Detailed </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94P50119A Moscow SEGODNYA in Russian 29 Mar 94 p 5 </F>
