<H3> <TI>   New Political Party Claims `Centrist' Orientation </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    New Political Party Claims `Centrist' Orientation </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944K1013B Baku VYSHKA in Russian 2 Apr 94 p 2 </F>
