<H3> <TI>   Novosibirsk Bankers Meet to Plan Development </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Novosibirsk Bankers Meet to Plan Development </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944F0526A Novosibirsk VECHERNIY NOVOSIBIRSK in Russian 31 
Mar 94 p 2 </F>

<F P=103> 944F0526A </F>
<F P=104>  Novosibirsk VECHERNIY NOVOSIBIRSK </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


